-- MOVES-SYZ Asset Management names Michael Clements as European equities head
-- 
-- Tue Sep 16, 2014 05:10AM EDT
-- None



Sept 16 (Reuters) - SYZ Asset Management, the institutional arm of Swiss banking group SYZ & Co [FINSYB.UL], appointed Michael Clements as head of European equities.

Clements will manage SYZ Asset Management's flagship funds Oyster European Opportunities, Oyster European Selection and Oyster Continental European Selection. Michael Clements will take over from Eric Bendahan, who has left for new opportunities after nine years at SYZ & Co.